        "long_text_mm4k2537": "Streamlines risk management for mortgage origination.",
        "long_text_mm4k4y1h": "Mortgage Secondary Marketing Traders",
        "long_text_mm4kh3fw": "The application automatically aggregates and publishes aggregate loan pipeline data as lenders originate loans, interacting with trade execution applications and other service providers over the network to eliminate manual efforts associated with managing mortgage risk.",
